snippet.title: SIMULACRA: Pipe Dreams - Announce Trailer
snippet.description: Your best friend tells you about a new game he is really into. He introduces it to you and while it seems harmless at first, something's not quite right. While the game offers temporary relief of life’s problems it also takes something away...
